# Some helpful Jam commands
# -q        : stop on failed target
# -jN       : use N cores
# -sVAR=VAL : Set VAR to VAL. Note that setting WINDOWS=false is the same as setting UNREAL=true,
#              frustratingly
# -dx       : print commands being used
# -n        : don't actually run commands
